data.description: The lifestyle you desire lives in this gorgeous home in a great location. Owner upgrades make it a standout in the neighborhood like a complete kitchen remodel, ceramic tile and wood laminate floors, extensive cabinets in the hall outside of and in the laundry room, sun room addition, solar screens, crown molding, driveway extension, A/C system, half bath addition, wood shutters in the owner’s suite and landscaping. The welcoming front porch is the perfect spot for welcoming guests to the huge floorplan with a combination formal living and dining room, and a family room with fireplace. The heart of this home is the huge island kitchen with tons of storage with pullout drawers, stainless steel appliances and double built-in ovens. The spacious owner’s suite bedroom has a wall of windows for great natural light and the bathroom has a corner jetted tub with separate shower. Extensive landscaping and a storage building make the backyard beautiful and efficient.
